+ I *HELPMENU: Line center
+ I *HELPMENU: Text "MOD+D  :  Run desktop program"
+ I *HELPMENU: Line center
+ I *HELPMENU: Text "MOD+R  :  Net RADIO Stations"
+ I *HELPMENU: Line center
+ I *HELPMENU: Text "MOD+V  :  VOLUME Control"
+ I *HELPMENU: Line center
+ I *HELPMENU: Line center
+ I *HELPMENU: Line center
+ I *HELPMENU: Line center
+ I *HELPMENU: Text "=-=-=-=-=-=-= WINDOWS MANAGEMENTS =-=-=-=-=-=-="
+ I *HELPMENU: Line center
+ I *HELPMENU: Line center
